-- Rabigh Refining Signs Accord to Provide Petrochemicals to Saudi Companies
-- Glen Carey
-- 2010-07-14T06:05:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/rabigh-refining-signs-accord-to-provide-petrochemicals-to-saudi-companies.html

          
          
             Rabigh Refining and Petrochemicals
Co., a joint venture between state-owned Saudi Aramco and
Sumitomo Chemical Co. of Japan, signed an agreement to provide
petrochemicals to Saudi Advanced Industries Co. and National
Industrialization Co., according to a statement on the Saudi
bourse website today.  
